Title: iLike Jake
Plot: After Jake, Carly's crush, agrees to sing a song on the webcast, Carly gets extremely excited. But, it is soon discovered that Jake is a terrible singer, so Carly asks Freddie to digitally enhance Jake's performance.
GuestStars: Doug Brochu (Wrestler #1),  Lexi Ainsworth (Lexi),  Joseph Buttler (Mr. Stern),  Austin Robert Butler (Jake Randall)
